library(lubridate)
## Warning: package 'lubridate' was built under R version 4.2.2
## Warning: package 'timechange' was built under R version 4.2.2
tlc <- tlc %>% 
  mutate(
    date_pickup = date(tpep_pickup_datetime),
    date_dropoff = date(tpep_dropoff_datetime),
    hour_pickup = hours(tpep_pickup_datetime), 
    hour_dropoff = hours(tpep_dropoff_datetime),
    weekday_pickup = wday(tpep_pickup_datetime, label = TRUE),
    day_pickup = day(tpep_pickup_datetime)
    )

tlc %>% group_by(weekday_pickup) %>% 
  tally %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = weekday_pickup, y = n)) + geom_bar(stat = "identity") 

tlc %>% group_by(day_pickup) %>% 
  tally %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = day_pickup, y = n)) + geom_line()

library(sf)
## Warning: package 'sf' was built under R version 4.2.2
library(ggmap)

tlc_zone <- st_read("taxi_zones/taxi_zones.shp", quiet = TRUE)
tlc_zone<-st_transform(tlc_zone,crs = 4326)

ggplot(tlc_zone) + geom_sf() + theme_inset() + theme_bw()

our_neighborhood<-tlc_zone%>%
  filter(zone=="Gramercy"|zone=="KipsBay")
ggplot(tlc_zone)+geom_sf()+theme_inset()+
  geom_sf(data=our_neighborhood,fill="red")

bbox<-st_bbox(tlc_zone)%>% as.numeric
nyc_map<-get_stamenmap(bbox=bbox,messaging = FALSE,zoom=11, maptype = "toner-lite",format=c("png"))
ggmap(nyc_map)+geom_sf(data = our_neighborhood,fill="red",inherit.aes = FALSE)

tlc_zone<-st_transform(tlc_zone,crs = 4326)
ggplot(tlc_zone)+geom_sf()+theme_inset()

pu_count<-tlc%>%
  group_by(PULocationID)%>% summarise(N=n())%>%
  rename(LocationID=PULocationID)
tlc_zone_new<-left_join(tlc_zone,pu_count,by="LocationID")

ggplot(tlc_zone_new %>% filter(borough=="Manhattan") )+geom_sf()+aes(fill=N)+scale_fill_viridis_c(option = "A")

ggmap(nyc_map)+geom_sf(data=tlc_zone_new,aes(fill=N),inherit.aes = FALSE)
